data.description: Quiet rural living in this recently updated home with  4-bedroom (including 1 non-conforming) residence with 2.5 baths. Every corner of this has been thoughtfully enhanced, from the freshly painted exterior to the granite countertops, doors, trim and even a high-end water purification system. Enjoy the serene views, while the fenced pasture stands ready for your animals. A detached garage/shop with a cozy wood stove and a charming barn add to the allure. Delight in cultivating your own harvest within the expansive, secure garden. This exceptional property is an absolute must-see, this is country living at it's finest.
